summary.about-summary: This is just general information about your primary world save, and some aggregate stats. If there's anything else in particular you'd like to see here or throughout the report, please let me know!
summary.need-help-or-have-questions: If you need help or have questions, please reach out to me on Discord (https://discord.gg/Zy3h6p7pA9) or open an issue on GitHub. I'm happy to help!

criticalErrors: No Level.sav file was found in your game save directory, but Paver did find a Level.sav.json file. Please ensure that a Level.sav file exists in your game save directory, or add `skipSavJsonConversion: true` to your config if you want Paver to use the Level.sav.json instead.
